order-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(211, 211, 211); border-right-width: 1px; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: rgb(211, 211, 211);\\" align=\\"center\\">&#39;sfHover&#39;</td></tr><tr style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\\"><td style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px; line-height: 26px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(211, 211, 211); border-right-width: 1px; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: rgb(211, 211, 211);\\" align=\\"center\\">pathClass</td><td style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px; line-height: 26px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(211, 211, 211); border-right-width: 1px; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: rgb(211, 211, 211);\\">设置当前项的样式，页面初始一个当前选中状态的样式</td><td style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px; line-height: 26px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(211, 211, 211); border-right-width: 1px; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: rgb(211, 211, 211);\\" align=\\"center\\">&#39;overideThisToUse&#39;</td></tr><tr style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\\"><td style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px; line-height: 26px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(211, 211, 211); border-right-width: 1px; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: rgb(211, 211, 211);\\" align=\\"center\\">delay</td><td style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px; line-height: 26px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(211, 211, 211); border-right-width: 1px; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: rgb(211, 211, 211);\\">鼠标离开下拉展开的菜单，等待关闭菜单的时间（毫秒）</td><td style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px; line-height: 26px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(211, 211, 211); border-right-width: 1px; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: rgb(211, 211, 211);\\" align=\\"center\\">800</td></tr><tr style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\\"><td style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px; line-height: 26px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(211, 211, 211); border-right-width: 1px; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: rgb(211, 211, 211);\\" align=\\"center\\">animation</td><td style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px; line-height: 26px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(211, 211, 211); border-right-width: 1px; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: rgb(211, 211, 211);\\">菜单展示效果</td><td style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px; line-height: 26px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(211, 211, 211); border-right-width: 1px; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: rgb(211, 211, 211);\\" align=\\"center\\">{opacity:&#39;show&#39;}</td></tr><tr style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\\"><td style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px; line-height: 26px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(211, 211, 211); border-right-width: 1px; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: rgb(211, 211, 211);\\" align=\\"center\\">speed</td><td style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px; line-height: 26px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(211, 211, 211); border-right-width: 1px; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: rgb(211, 211, 211);\\">设置菜单展开速度，可以为&#39;slow&#39;,&#39;fast&#39;,&#39;normal&#39;</td><td style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px; line-height: 26px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(211, 211, 211); border-right-width: 1px; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: rgb(211, 211, 211);\\" align=\\"center\\">&#39;normal&#39;</td></tr><tr style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\\"><td style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px; line-height: 26px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(211, 211, 211); border-right-width: 1px; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: rgb(211, 211, 211);\\" align=\\"center\\">disableHI</td><td style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px; line-height: 26px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(211, 211, 211); border-right-width: 1px; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: rgb(211, 211, 211);\\">设置为true时，则不支持hoverIntent插件</td><td style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px; line-height: 26px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(211, 211, 211); border-right-width: 1px; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: rgb(211, 211, 211);\\" align=\\"center\\">true</td></tr></tbody></table><p style=\\"margin: 6px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Tahoma, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\\">superfish插件还可以支持回调函数，支持hoverIntent插件，在有hoverIntent插件的情况下执行hoverIntent而忽视淡入淡出效果。如果基于某种原因在你使用superfish时不想使用hoverIntent，将disableHI设置为 &quot;true&quot;。</p><p style=\\"margin: 6px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Tahoma, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\\">此外当遇到select标签时，为了不让下拉菜单被select遮挡，需要调用另一个插件：<a target=\\"_blank\\" href=\\"http://plugins.jquery.com/project/bgiframe\\" style=\\"margin: 4px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 102, 153); text-decoration: underline;\\">bgiframe</a>，使用方法：</p><pre style=\\"margin: 6px auto; padding: 4px; border-width: 1px 1px 1px 5px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(215, 215, 215); font-size: 12px; white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(250, 250, 250) none repeat scroll 0% 0%;\\"><code class=\\"js\\" style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\\">$(<span class=\\"js__string\\" style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: teal;\\">&quot;ul.sf-menu&quot;</span>).superfish().find(<span class=\\"js__string\\" style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: teal;\\">&#39;ul&#39;</span>).bgIframe(<span class=\\"js__brace\\" style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: red; font-weight: bold;\\">{</span>opacity:false<span class=\\"js__brace\\" style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: red; font-weight: bold;\\">}</span>); <br/></code></pre>', 'superfish是一款可以制作多级下拉菜单的jquery插件，支持水平和垂直方向的菜单，下拉的菜单不会被标签select遮挡，支持动态下拉效果，如垂直向下伸展，支持阴影效果（IE6除外），用户可定制样式。', '菜单', '', 7, '/article/20160418/thumb_pwUprbxZrM8W9HhZu7bs.jpg', 29, 0, 1460960123, 0, 1),
	(63, 0, '使用AD Gallery制作强大的相册画廊', 58, '慵懒时光', '<p><img alt=\\"ad-gallery.jpg\\" src=\\"/Uploads/Lazy/Public/Common/ueditor/image/20160418/57147bd0144b8.jpg\\" title=\\"57147bd0144b8.jpg\\"/></p><h4 style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: 36px; line-height: 36px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Tahoma, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\\">主要特性：</h4><p style=\\"margin: 6px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Tahoma, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\\">可以选择不同的展示效果，如上下左右滑动、淡入淡出、缩放交替等效果。</p><p style=\\"margin: 6px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Tahoma, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\\">支持键盘方向键切换。</p><p style=\\"margin: 6px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Tahoma, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\\">图片左右导航。</p><p style=\\"margin: 6px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Tahoma, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\\">预加载图像，直到完全显示。</p><p style=\\"margin: 6px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Tahoma, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\\">支持自动播放和暂停。</p><p style=\\"margin: 6px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Tahoma, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\\">可设置照片标题和描述信息。</p><p style=\\"margin: 6px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Tahoma, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; ba